Amendment No. 2 to HB0377
Johnson
Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 376 House Bill No. 377*
by deleting subsection (a) in Section 1 and substituting:
(a) As used in this section:
(1) "Institution" means a four-year public or private institution of higher
education located in this state; and
(2) "Legacy preference" means a preference in admission given to an
applicant by an institution based on the applicant's familial relationship to an
alumnus of the institution.
AND FURTHER AMEND by redesignating subsections (e) and (f) in Section 1 as subsections
(f) and (g) and adding the following as a new subsection (e):
(e) An institution shall not confer a legacy preference on an applicant for
admission to the institution.
